title: Various Artists - Caferino Albuquerque Vol. 7 [trip-hop]
description:
It&#039;s been a long while since the last Caferino Albuquerque volume. Assuming that someone still cares and there aren&#039;t just leechers that are new to the series... but, in the end, does it matter? Like the other volumes, the tracklisting of this 7th volume had to came about naturally, and in a moment when I could afford to leave the computer on for uploading. Not as many new artists as I promised quite a while ago, but the tracklisting sure is hot.
